 :tx/rationale "Create task: CCE-1: Embedding infrastructure — integrate model2vec/potion-128M for local semantic embeddings. CONTEXT: The information-theoretic bottleneck at the LLM→braid interface: keyword tokenization reduces ~100K bits of semantic information to ~100 bits. Embeddings preserve semantic similarity as geometric proximity — two observations about the same concept have nearby vectors even with zero keyword overlap. RATIONALE: This is the enabling technology for concept crystallization. Without embeddings, concept formation requires keyword heuristics that fail on synonym relationships (the exact DOGFOOD failure). With embeddings, concept formation is cosine similarity in a learned semantic space — the same space the LLM natively operates in. APPROACH: (1) Add frankensearch-embed (or model2vec crate directly) as optional dependency to braid-kernel Cargo.toml, feature-gated behind 'embeddings' feature flag. (2) Create crates/braid-kernel/src/embedding.rs (~200 LOC). Core API: pub fn embed_text(text: &str) -> Option<Vec<f32>> — returns 256-dim vector from potion-128M. Returns None if model not available (graceful degradation). pub fn cosine_similarity(a: &[f32], b: &[f32]) -> f32. pub fn centroid(vectors: &[&[f32]]) -> Vec<f32> — running mean. pub fn variance(vectors: &[&[f32]], centroid: &[f32]) -> f32 — intra-cluster distance. (3) Add schema attribute :exploration/embedding (Bytes, One) to Layer 3 schema. The 256 f32 values serialize as 1024 bytes. (4) Model loading: lazy-load from .braid/.cache/potion-128m.safetensors on first embed_text() call. If file doesn't exist, embed_text returns None (fallback to Jaccard). Model file is ~5MB. (5) IMPORTANT: The embedding is a STATIC embedder — vocabulary lookup + mean-pooling, not a neural network forward pass. No GPU required. Deterministic. Same input always produces same output. This is C8 compatible — the kernel doesn't depend on a specific model; the model is policy-layer configuration. ACCEPTANCE: (A) embed_text('hello world') returns Some(vec) with 256 elements. (B) cosine_similarity of identical texts = 1.0. (C) cosine_similarity of semantically similar texts (event sourcing, event replay) > 0.7. (D) cosine_similarity of unrelated texts (event sourcing, SQL injection) < 0.3. (E) embed_text returns None when model file absent (no panic). (F) Embedding is deterministic: same text → same vector. (G) Embedding latency < 2ms per text. (H) Feature flag: cargo build without 'embeddings' feature compiles and runs (Jaccard fallback). FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/embedding.rs (new), crates/braid-kernel/Cargo.toml, crates/braid-kernel/src/lib.rs. TRACES-TO: ADR-FOUNDATION-015 (Observer Formalism — expanding the epistemological horizon with a new observer capability)."
